line_1: Cut the good cord — a traitor of the gang.
line_2: There to expire; — but one who saw him hang

line_1: Admits Him in among the Gang:
But how the subject theme may gang,
line_2: Perhaps it may turn out a Sang;

line_1: The Poets too, a venal gang,
line_2: Wad gar you trow ye ne'er do wrang,
